title: Senior Bowl Breakdown with Ryan Wilson (Football 1/24)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by CBS Sports NFL Draft Expert Ryan Wilson to break down the latest news and notes around the NFL, including Larry Fitzgerald returning for a 16th season and Derek Carr wanting to fight Max Kellerman. Then the guys break down everything Ryan's hearing and seeing from the Senior Bowl in Mobile, Alabama.
